I’ve just looked it up, and it seems like Helvetica, Helvetica Neue, or  
their custom versions are used in (in no particular order):

- [Milan](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/oinoi.files.wordpress.com/2008/01/17_metro2.jpg?w=490);
- [Chicago](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/media.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/uploader/images/signs/blue-line-of-chicago/full_blue-line-of-chicago.jpg);
- [Budapest](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/media.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/uploader/images/signs/changing-line/full_changing_line.jpg);
- [Tehran](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/4.bp.blogspot.com/-N1VCDqFmNGY/UIdvlnlhhUI/AAAAAAAABGw/3qifOZDquSI/s1600/IR.Teh38.JPG);
- [Barcelona](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/33/Artiques_-_Sant_Adri%C3%A0.JPG); 
- [Vienna](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/farm6.staticflickr.com/5068/5786467041_393e54f57a_b.jpg);
- [Toronto](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/media.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/uploader/images/signs/subway-elevator/full_subway-elevator.jpg);
- [Washington](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/www.pinterest.com/robbietemplon/dc-metro-signs/); 
- [Melbourne](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/media.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/uploader/images/signs/melbourne-subway-station/full_melbourne-subway-station.jpg);
- [Madrid](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/farm1.staticflickr.com/14/14843100_077700f8d8_b.jpg); 
- [Helsinki](http://web.archive.org/web/20150123062659/http:/www.urbanrail.net/eu/fi/helsinki/kalasatama2.jpg)…

There should be a lot more…
